#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma 5.21"
msgstr "Plasma 5.21"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Systemsettings"
msgstr "Sistemske nastavitve"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "system notification"
msgstr "sistemsko obvestilo"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "notification"
msgstr "obvestilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&plasma;, like all applications, needs to inform the user when a problem "
"occurs, a task is completed, or something has happened. &plasma; uses a set "
"of <quote>System Notifications</quote> to keep the user informed on what is "
"happening."
msgstr ""
"&plasma;, tako kot vse aplikacije, mora obvestiti uporabnika, ko se pojavi "
"težava, je opravilo dokončano ali se kaj zgodi. &plasma; uporablja nabor "
"<quote>Sistemska obvestila</quote>, da uporabnika obvešča o tem, kaj se "
"dogaja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using this module, you can determine what &plasma; does to communicate each "
"event."
msgstr "S tem modulom lahko določite, kaj &plasma; sporoča za vsak dogodek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notification Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve obvestil"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do Not Disturb mode"
msgstr "Način Ne moti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode disables all visual and most audible notifications to let you "
"focus on your current task. Settings in this section let you configure under "
"which circumstances &plasma; automatically enables do not disturb mode."
msgstr ""
"Ta način onemogoči vsa vizualna in večino zvočnih obvestil, da se lahko "
"osredotočite na svojo trenutno nalogo. Nastavitve v tem razdelku vam "
"omogočajo, da konfigurirate, v katerih okoliščinah &plasma; samodejno "
"omogoči način Ne moti."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable when screens are mirrored"
msgstr "Omogoči, ko so zasloni zrcaljeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically enable do not disturb mode when you mirror your screens, for "
"example during a presentation."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno omogočite način Ne moti, ko zrcalite svoje zaslone, na primer med "
"predstavitvijo."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable while screen sharing"
msgstr "Omogoči med deljenjem zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically enable do not disturb mode when you share your screens, for "
"example during an online lecture."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno omogočite način Ne moti, ko delite svoje zaslone, na primer med "
"spletnim predavanjem."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable while a fullscreen application is focused"
msgstr "Omogoči, ko je celozaslonska aplikacija v fokusu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically enable do not disturb mode while you are using a fullscreen "
"application, for example watching a video."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno omogoči način Ne moti, medtem ko uporabljate celozaslonsko "
"aplikacijo, na primer med gledanjem videa."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show critical notifications"
msgstr "Prikaži kritična obvestila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to show critical notifications, such as your battery is almost "
"empty, to show even when in do not disturb mode."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se kritična obvestila, kot je na primer, da je baterija skoraj "
"prazna, prikažejo tudi v načinu \"ne moti\"."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle with:"
msgstr "Preklopi z:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A global shortcut you can press to enable and disable do not disturb mode "
"anytime."
msgstr ""
"Globalna bližnjica, ki jo lahko kadar koli pritisnete, da omogočite ali "
"onemogočite način Ne moti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filters"
msgstr "Filtri"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Critical notifications: <guiicon>Always keep on top</guiicon>"
msgstr "Kritična obvestila: <guiicon>Vedno bodi na vrhu</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep critical notifications, such as your battery is almost empty, always on "
"top. This ensures they will also be visible while watching a fullscreen "
"video or giving a presentation."
msgstr ""
"Naj bodo kritična obvestila, kot je baterija skoraj prazna, vedno na vrhu. "
"To zagotavlja, da bodo vidni tudi med gledanjem celozaslonskega videa ali "
"predstavitvijo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal notifications: <guiicon>Always keep on top</guiicon>"
msgstr "Običajna obvestila: <guiicon>Vedno ostani na vrhu</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep normal notifications, such as messages, always on top. This ensures "
"they will also be visible while watching a fullscreen video or giving a "
"presentation."
msgstr ""
"Naj bodo običajna obvestila, kot so sporočila, vedno na vrhu. To zagotavlja, "
"da bodo vidni tudi med gledanjem celozaslonskega videa ali predstavitvijo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Low priority notifications: <guiicon>Show popup</guiicon> and <guiicon>Show "
"in history</guiicon>"
msgstr ""
"Obvestila nizke prioritete: <guiicon>Pokaži pojavno okno</guiicon> in "
"<guiicon>Pokaži v zgodovini</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether low priority notifications, such as track changes in your media "
"player, will be shown as popups or in the history, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Ali se bodo obvestila z nizko prioriteto, kot so spremembe skladbe v "
"medijskem predvajalniku, prikazovala v obliki pojavnih oken ali v zgodovini."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Behavior"
msgstr "Vedenje"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Popup: <guiicon>Show near notification icon</guiicon>"
msgstr "Pojavno okno: <guiicon>Prikaži ikono obvestila v bližini</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show notification popups close to where your notification icon is located in "
"your panel."
msgstr ""
"Pokažite pojavna okna z obvestili blizu mesta, kjer se na plošči nahaja vaša "
"ikona za obvestila."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose…"
msgstr "Izberite…"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you choose a fixed screen corner where notification popups will be "
"positioned."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro fiksnega kota zaslona, ​​kjer bodo postavljena pojavna okna z "
"obvestili."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide after:"
msgstr "Skrij po:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After how many seconds the notification popup will automatically disappear. "
"You can choose anywhere between 1 and 120 seconds."
msgstr ""
"Po koliko sekundah bo pojavno okno z obvestilom samodejno izginilo. Izberete "
"lahko med 1 in 120 sekundami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Progress and Badges"
msgstr "Napredek aplikacije in značke"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application progress"
msgstr "Napredek aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Options in this section control how application progress, such as copying or "
"downloading a file, is presented."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti v tem razdelku nadzirajo, kako je predstavljen napredek aplikacije, "
"kot je kopiranje ali prenos datoteke."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:136 index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show in task manager"
msgstr "Prikaži v upravljalniku opravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colorize the window in the panel based on the progress."
msgstr "Pobarvaj okno v plošči glede na napredek."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show in notifications"
msgstr "Prikaži v obvestilih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a notification popup during the progress."
msgstr "Prikaži pojavno obvestilo med napredovanjem."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep popup open during progress"
msgstr "Ohrani pojavno okno odprto med napredovanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether the popup should remain visible for the entire duration of the "
"progress or automatically hide. It will always be shown again when the task "
"finishes or fails."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj pojavno okno ostane vidno ves čas trajanja napredka ali naj se "
"samodejno skrije. Vedno se znova prikaže, ko se opravilo konča ali ne uspe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notification badges"
msgstr "Značke za obvestila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let applications show badges, such as an unread message count, in the panel."
msgstr ""
"Naj aplikacije na plošči prikažejo značke, kot je število neprebranih "
"sporočil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guilabel>Configure...</guilabel> button at the end of the list "
"opens the application settings page which lets you configure notification "
"behavior on a per-application and per-service basis."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guilabel>Konfiguriraj ...</guilabel> na koncu seznama se "
"odpre stran z nastavitvami aplikacije, ki vam omogoča konfiguracijo vedenja "
"obvestil za vsako aplikacijo in storitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the sidebar on the left to choose an entry from the "
"<guilabel>Applications</guilabel> or <guilabel>System Services</guilabel> "
"category."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite stransko vrstico na levi, da izberete vnos iz kategorije "
"<guilabel>Aplikacije</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Sistemske storitve</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"General warning popups as well as startup and shutdown sounds are located "
"under the <guilabel>Plasma Workspace</guilabel> service."
msgstr ""
"Splošna pojavna okna z opozorili ter zvoki za zagon in zaustavitev se "
"nahajajo pod storitvijo <guilabel>Plasma Workspace</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applications that do not provide proper identification, such as shell "
"scripts, can be configured using the <guilabel>Other Applications</guilabel> "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacije, ki ne zagotavljajo ustrezne identifikacije, kot so lupinska "
"skripta, lahko konfigurirate z vnosom <guilabel>Druge aplikacije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show popups"
msgstr "Prikaži pojavna okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether this application may show popup notifications."
msgstr "Ali lahko ta aplikacija prikazuje pojavna obvestila."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show in do not disturb mode"
msgstr "Prikaži v načinu ne moti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether this application may show popup notifications even when in do not "
"disturb mode."
msgstr ""
"Ali lahko ta aplikacija prikazuje pojavna obvestila tudi v načinu Ne moti."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show in history"
msgstr "Pokaži v zgodovini"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether this application's notifications will be kept in the notification "
"history."
msgstr "Ali bodo obvestila te aplikacije shranjena v zgodovini obvestil."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show notification badges"
msgstr "Pokaži značke za obvestila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether this application may show badges, such as an unread message count, "
"in the panel."
msgstr ""
"Ali lahko ta aplikacija na plošči prikaže značke, kot je število neprebranih "
"sporočil."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure Events..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj dogodke..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For &kde; applications you can also configure each notification individually."
msgstr "Za &kde; aplikacije lahko tudi konfigurirate vsako obvestilo posebej."

#~ msgid "Custom…"
#~ msgstr "Po meri…"

#~ msgid "Choose Custom Position..."
#~ msgstr "Izberi položaj po meri ..."
